  "text": "where × denotes the usual cross product in R 3 , while T and F denote, respectively, the external torque and the external force applied to the body. To help the reader distinguish between the different systems and subsystems considered throughout the paper, we shall call \"system (Π, P )\" the control system [CITATION_1] .",
